gobblin.metastore.nameParser

Interface DatasetUrnStateStoreNameParser

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    GuidDatasetUrnStateStoreNameParser, SimpleDatasetUrnStateStoreNameParser

    public interface DatasetUrnStateStoreNameParser
    Parses datasetUrns to dataset state store name. This is useful for systems that have limit on the length of the state store name.
